OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FAthletes from around the world arrived
OL,7,Fat Glasgow's Hydro arena for this
OL,8,Fyear's Commonwealth Games, which are
OL,9,Fbeing held at a reduced-cost model to
OL,10,Fensure the games have a future, ITV
OL,11,FNews Scotland Reporter Louise Scott
OL,12,Freports
OL,14,FThe King and Queen made a dramatic
OL,15,Fentrance at the Glasgow Commonwealth
OL,16,FGames opening ceremony, stepping out
OL,17,Fof the Tardis as the 11-day sporting
OL,18,Fevent got underway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
