PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FCharles and Camilla played a prominent
OL,7,Frole in the opening ceremony at
OL,8,FGlasgow's Hydro arena.
OL,10,FMore than 3,000 athletes from 74
OL,11,Fnations and territories will compete
OL,12,Facross 10 sports and six Para sports.
OL,14,FAhead of the opening ceremony,
OL,15,FCommonwealth Games mascot Finnie, a
OL,16,Funicorn inspired by Scotland's
OL,17,Fnational animal, entertained the crowd
OL,18,Fduring the pre-show, while Scottish
OL,19,Fwrestler Grado made an appearance
OL,20,Fdressed as a teacake.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FThe ceremony began with a film showing
OL,7,Fthe Doctor Who's famous telephone box
OL,8,Ftravelling across Scotland.
OL,10,FThe Tardis was piloted by cycling
OL,11,Flegend Sir Chris Hoy and actor Greg
OL,12,FMcHugh, much to the confusion of the
OL,13,FSeventh Doctor, Sylvester McCoy.
OL,15,FAfter visiting several famous Scottish
OL,16,Flandmarks, the Tardis arrived at
OL,17,FBalmoral Castle before materialising
OL,18,Finside Glasgow's Hydro arena in an on-
OL,19,Fstage garden.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FThe King and Queen then emerged from
OL,7,Fthe Tardis and walked down a ramp
OL,8,Fbefore taking their seats in the royal
OL,9,Fbox.
OL,11,FAfter the parade of athletes from the
OL,12,FCommonwealth nations taking part in
OL,13,Fthe Games, actor Sam Heughan shared
OL,14,Fthe stage with an animatronic Loch
OL,15,FNess monster in the next segment of
OL,16,Fthe show.
OL,18,FSinger Nathan Evans performed Scotland
OL,19,FIs A Place Called Home amid energetic
OL,20,Fflashmob dancers representing the
OL,21,Fpeople of Glasgow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FAt the end of the ceremony, the King's
OL,7,Fbaton arrived at the arena.
OL,9,FThe baton contained a chamber for the
OL,10,FKing's message, which was placed
OL,11,Finside in March 2025 before it
OL,12,Ftravelled around the world as part of
OL,13,Fa 500-day multinational relay.
OL,15,FThe King then stood to formally
OL,16,Fdeclare the Games open.
OL,18,FHe said: "As we gather, we celebrate
OL,19,Fthe dedication and talent of every
OL,20,Fathlete and team.
OL,26,@zD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F"Your perseverance inspires us, and we
OL,7,Feagerly anticipate your achievements
OL,8,Fin the coming days.
OL,10,F"For these Games, the relay has
OL,11,Fcarried another message ` to help
OL,12,Fremove the plastic pollution that
OL,13,Fharms our oceans and waterways, and
OL,14,Fcan impact on human health.
OL,16,F"Addressing plastic pollution
OL,17,Fcomplements the immense global efforts
OL,18,Frequired to protect 30% of the world's
OL,19,Focean by 2030."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
