OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FThe Glasgow Commonwealth Games is not
OL,7,Fthe first time a monarch has made a
OL,8,Fmemorable entrance at the opening
OL,9,Fceremony of a major sporting event.
OL,11,FQueen Elizabeth II famously appeared
OL,12,Fin the London 2012 Olympics opening
OL,13,Fceremony, seemingly skydiving into the
OL,14,Fstadium with James Bond actor Daniel
OL,15,FCraig after he escorted her from
OL,16,FBuckingham Palace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FHer stunt double jumped above the
OL,7,Farena wearing a dress with sewn-in
OL,8,FVictorian-style bloomers and a large
OL,9,Fzip at the back to accommodate a
OL,10,Fparachute.
OL,12,FThe late Queen also appeared in a
OL,13,Fcomedy sketch with a digitally
OL,14,Fanimated Paddington Bear to mark her
OL,15,FPlatinum Jubilee, in which she
OL,16,Frevealed she kept marmalade sandwiches
OL,17,F- Paddington's favourite treat - in
OL,18,Fher handbag.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
