OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FThis year marks the fourth time the
OL,7,Fgames have been held in Scotland, with
OL,8,Fthe last being 2014. Birmingham also
OL,9,Fhosted the quad-annual event in 2022.
OL,11,FThe 2026 games was originally meant to
OL,12,Fbe held in the Australian state of
OL,13,FVictoria, however the would-be hosts
OL,14,Fwithdrew in July 2023 over concerns
OL,15,Faround increasing costs.
OL,17,FVictoria had agreed to host the event
OL,18,Fa year earlier, after the Commonwealth
OL,19,FGames Federation (CGF) struggled to
OL,20,Ffind a host.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FThe cost was originally estimated to
OL,7,Fbe A$2.6bn (#1.35 billion), but the
OL,8,Fprojected bill soared to more than A$6
OL,9,Fbillion (#3.11 billion).
OL,11,FAfter discussions with numerous
OL,12,Fdifferent cities, Glasgow was
OL,13,Fconfirmed as the replacement host city
OL,14,Fin September 2024, albeit with a
OL,15,Fscaled-back version to keep costs down.
OL,17,FThe overall size of the 2026 event
OL,18,Fwill be noticeably smaller.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FThe Scotstoun Stadium, which will be
OL,7,Fhome to several athletic events, will
OL,8,Fhost just 11,000 spectators, down from
OL,9,Fthe 50,000 cheering on competitors in
OL,10,Fthe 2014 Games.
OL,12,FThe money being spent on these games
OL,13,Fis also down. In 2014 the budget came
OL,14,Fto #543 million, but the 2026 Games
OL,15,Fare set to cost just #150 million,
OL,16,Fwith no public money being spent on
OL,17,Fthe event at all.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FThe Commonwealth Games Foundation
OL,7,F(CGF) is investing #100m of this, with
OL,8,Fthe remainder coming from ticketing,
OL,9,Fsponsorship, broadcast rights and
OL,10,Fmerchandise.
OL,12,FWhile visiting Glasgow, the Burnham
OL,13,Fmet the first ministers of Scotland
OL,14,Fand Wales in a bid to strengthen ties
OL,15,Fwith the devolved nations.
OL,17,FWales' First Minister Rhun ap
OL,18,FIorwerth, leader of Plaid Cymru, said:
OL,19,F"I'm very pleased that we were able to
OL,20,Forganise this first face-to-face
OL,21,Fmeeting so soon.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F"We had a conversation on Tuesday but
OL,7,Fit was important that I had that
OL,8,Fopportunity to congratulate him and
OL,9,Ftalk about the ways that we hope to be
OL,10,Fable to cooperate on the non-devolved
OL,11,Fareas."
OL,13,FHe added: "It's a new chapter with a
OL,14,Fnew Prime Minister. My job is to make
OL,15,Fsure that it's a chapter that reads as
OL,16,Fa good story for Wales."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@GO]uD@KOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FDetailing Burnham's conversation with
OL,7,FScottish First Minister John Swinney,
OL,8,Fa Downing Street spokesperson said:
OL,9,F"The prime minister began by
OL,10,Fcongratulating the first minister and
OL,11,Fthe city of Glasgow for hosting the
OL,12,FCommonwealth Games, especially at
OL,13,Fshort notice, and said he was looking
OL,14,Fforward to watching the opening
OL,15,Fceremony later that evening.
OL,17,F"The conversation then turned to how
OL,18,Fthe Prime Minister and First Minister
OL,19,Fcan work more closely together to
OL,20,Fbuild a model of devolution to improve
OL,21,Fpeople's lives across Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F"The prime minister reiterated his
OL,7,Fbelief that deeper devolution could
OL,8,Fmake a real difference in helping
OL,9,Fcommunities across the UK to re-
OL,10,Findustrialise - creating jobs,
OL,11,Ftransforming high streets and reviving
OL,12,Flocal economies - and welcomed the
OL,13,FFirst Minister's willingness to engage
OL,14,Fwith that process.
OL,16,F"The prime minister stated up front
OL,17,Fthat another referendum on
OL,18,Findependence was off limits because it
OL,19,Fwould take our focus away from growing
OL,20,Fthe economy and helping families with
OL,21,Fthe cost of living.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784918934
OL,3,CKing and Queen emerge from Tardis to
OL,4,Cbegin Glasgow Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F"More broadly, the Prime Minister said
OL,7,Fthis was a moment for both sides to
OL,8,Fwork together in a constructive
OL,9,Frelationship. He looked forward to
OL,10,Fregular engagement with the First
OL,11,FMinister in the months ahead."
